Ultimately Rabbi Wolpe says that the Jewish people are a "religious family".

Of course, scientifically speaking, a racial group is basically a large extended family group.

"Judaism is effectively a breeding protocol....There's a very strange moment when you sign up for '23 and Me'...and you get a DNA test result that tells you how Jewish you are"
(at 12 min) https://youtu.be/3mSxiFUzZ-Q?t=718
